{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/processus/layout,_N_T_/processus/page,_N_T_/processus"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--UZSX2TIPZxv9mSgYDsEIa--><html lang=\"fr\" class=\"scroll-smooth\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/13971731025ec697-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/8a1d8947e5852e30-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/eaead17c7dbfcd5d-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/eff3f172c821293a.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-b24e2ce1453fbcbb.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-38b49df12a94ee57.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-81a43faefea5ce3a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/619-ba102abea3e3d0e4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-39bd8138fb29828d.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>GOLD - Investissement Visionnaire</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Plateforme d&#x27;investissement pour l&#x27;Afrique francophone\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/x-icon\" sizes=\"16x16\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"__variable_0a80b4 __variable_744198 __variable_0d7163 antialiased bg-bg text-text-1 flex flex-col min-h-screen\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><nav class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 w-full z-50 transition-all duration-500 px-4 md:px-6 bg-transparent py-5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center\"><a class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-1\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"font-syne text-white tracking-[0.35em] text-[15px] font-light\">GOLDEN</span><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-7 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-gold opacity-80\"></div><span class=\"font-syne text-gold tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px]\">INVEST</span><div class=\"w-7 h-px bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-gold opacity-80\"></div></div></a><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-2\"><a class=\"text-[12px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full border transition-all duration-300\n                  text-bg bg-gold border-gold font-bold\" href=\"/processus\">Processus</a><a class=\"text-[12px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full border transition-all duration-300\n                  text-white/60 border-transparent hover:text-white hover:bg-gold/10 hover:border-gold/30\" href=\"/projets\">Projets</a><a class=\"text-[12px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full border transition-all duration-300\n                  text-white/60 border-transparent hover:text-white hover:bg-gold/10 hover:border-gold/30\" href=\"/profils\">Réseau</a><a class=\"text-[12px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] px-5 py-2 rounded-full border transition-all duration-300\n                  text-white/60 border-transparent hover:text-white hover:bg-gold/10 hover:border-gold/30\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-4\"><a class=\"text-[12px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-transparent hover:border-white/20\" href=\"/login\">Connexion</a><a class=\"px-6 py-2.5 text-[11px] font-syne font-bold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full bg-gold text-bg hover:bg-gold-light transition-all\" href=\"/deposer\">Commencer</a></div><div class=\"flex md:hidden items-center gap-2\"><a class=\"text-[11px] font-syne uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-all px-3 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 hover:border-white/30\" href=\"/login\">Connexion</a><button class=\"relative z-[110] text-white hover:text-gold transition-colors p-2 touch-manipulation\" aria-label=\"Ouvrir le menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex-grow w-full\"><main class=\"pt-32 pb-20 bg-bg\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-playfair text-white mb-8 text-center\">Un processus <span class=\"text-gold\">d&#x27;excellence</span></h1><p class=\"text-text-2 text-center mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Découvrez comment nous simplifions l&#x27;accès au capital pour les entrepreneurs et l&#x27;accès aux opportunités pour les investisseurs.</p><div class=\"space-y-12 mb-32\"><div class=\"flex gap-8 items-start border-l border-gold/20 pl-8 relative group\"><div class=\"absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-gold rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(46,125,50,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\"></div><div><span class=\"text-gold font-syne font-bold text-xl\">01</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-white font-playfair mt-2 mb-4 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Inscription &amp; KYC</h3><p class=\"text-text-2 leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Créez votre compte en quelques clics. Pour les investisseurs, une vérification d&#x27;identité (KYC) est nécessaire pour garantir la conformité et la sécurité des transactions.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 items-start border-l border-gold/20 pl-8 relative group\"><div class=\"absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-gold rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(46,125,50,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\"></div><div><span class=\"text-gold font-syne font-bold text-xl\">02</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-white font-playfair mt-2 mb-4 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Soumission / Exploration</h3><p class=\"text-text-2 leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Porteurs de projets : soumettez votre pitch deck et vos prévisions financières. Investisseurs : parcourez les projets vérifiés par notre comité de sélection.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 items-start border-l border-gold/20 pl-8 relative group\"><div class=\"absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-gold rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(46,125,50,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\"></div><div><span class=\"text-gold font-syne font-bold text-xl\">03</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-white font-playfair mt-2 mb-4 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Mise en relation</h3><p class=\"text-text-2 leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Accédez à une dataroom sécurisée pour consulter les documents confidentiels. Échangez avec les fondateurs via notre interface de messagerie chiffrée.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-8 items-start border-l border-gold/20 pl-8 relative group\"><div class=\"absolute -left-[9px] top-0 w-4 h-4 bg-gold rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(46,125,50,0.6)] group-hover:scale-125 transition-transform\"></div><div><span class=\"text-gold font-syne font-bold text-xl\">04</span><h3 class=\"text-2xl text-white font-playfair mt-2 mb-4 group-hover:text-gold transition-colors\">Investissement</h3><p class=\"text-text-2 leading-relaxed opacity-80\">Signez les documents juridiques électroniquement et transférez les fonds via nos partenaires bancaires sécurisés. Le suivi est assuré par GOLDEN INVEST.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface p-10 rounded-3xl border border-gold/10\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-playfair text-white mb-10 text-center\">Questions Fréquentes</h2><div class=\"grid gap-8\"><div class=\"border-b border-gold/10 pb-6 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-syne mb-3 font-bold flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 border border-gold/40 flex items-center justify-center text-gold text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0\">1</span>Quels sont les critères de sélection ?</h4><p class=\"text-text-2 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-9\">Nous analysons la viabilité du business model, l&#x27;expérience de l&#x27;équipe et l&#x27;impact potentiel sur le marché local.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-gold/10 pb-6 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-syne mb-3 font-bold flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 border border-gold/40 flex items-center justify-center text-gold text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0\">2</span>Est-ce sécurisé ?</h4><p class=\"text-text-2 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-9\">Toutes les données sont chiffrées et les transactions passent par des institutions financières certifiées.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-gold/10 pb-6 last:border-0 last:pb-0\"><h4 class=\"text-white font-syne mb-3 font-bold flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-gold/20 border border-gold/40 flex items-center justify-center text-gold text-xs font-bold flex-shrink-0\">3</span>Combien ça coûte ?</h4><p class=\"text-text-2 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-9\">Le dépôt de projet est gratuit. Une commission est prélevée uniquement lors de la réussite de la levée de fonds.</p></div></div></div></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"bg-bg border-t border-white/10 pt-28 pb-14 px-6 font-sans relative\"><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[200px] bg-gold/10 blur-[140px] pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 mb-20\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 border-2 border-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-gold text-lg\">G</div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide\">Golden <span class=\"text-gold\">Invest</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs\">Plateforme d’investissement stratégique dédiée à connecter investisseurs et porteurs de projets au Bénin et en Afrique.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"text-gold mb-6 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest\">Navigation</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-gold transition\" href=\"/projets\">Projets</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-gold transition\" href=\"/processus\">Méthode</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-gold transition\" href=\"/profils\">Réseau</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-gold mb-6 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest\">Support</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-white/80\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-gold transition\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-gold transition\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-gold mb-6 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest\">Bureaux</h4><p class=\"text-white/80 text-sm leading-loose\">Cotonou - Haie Vive <br/>Porto-Novo - Zone Admin <br/><span class=\"text-gold\">contact@golden-invest.com</span></p></div></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-10 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6\"><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-xs tracking-widest text-center md:text-left\">© 2026 GOLDEN INVEST — Tous droits réservés</p><div class=\"flex gap-6 text-white/60 text-sm\"><span class=\"hover:text-gold cursor-pointer transition\">Facebook</span><span class=\"hover:text-gold cursor-pointer transition\">LinkedIn</span><span class=\"hover:text-gold cursor-pointer transition\">WhatsApp</span></div></div></footer><script src=